A photo posted by Whitney Port (@whitneyeveport) on Feb 9, 2017 at 2:49pm PST WATCH: Whitney Port Marries Longtime Fiance Tim Rosenman in Palm Springs Port and Rosenman, an associate producer on her Hills spinoff, The City , tied the knot in November 2015, in a gorgeous Palm Springs, California, ceremony. ET caught up with the 31-year-old fashion designer last May, where she opened up about starting a family. "I'm happily married. I'd love to eventually start a family and become a mom," she revealed. "[It won't be] happening in the super near future, but definitely something that I would love to be able to do." Port isn't the only Hills alum expecting a bundle of joy. In fact, Port's BFF, Lauren Conrad, announced that she was pregnant with her first child last month in a special New Year's message to fans. See the first photo of LC's baby bump in the video below.
